<hr size=1> So what are your thoughts on Naggy and Vox raids on which the books are reserved? Do you still go in hopes of a second book drop, or getting to roll on a COF?<br>
<br>
What about the items that are traditionally given to specific classes? (IE bag to monks) Should an item that is all/all be lottoed to everyone? Including the CoF? <br>
<br>
Ive seen his done a number of ways, I think my favorite was the following. (Naggy loots here as example)<br>
<br>
If you can Equip, you can roll: (Yes that means everyone can roll on the bag including casters)<br>
<br>
Exception is melee can only roll on CoF<br>
<br>
Scale is rolled among warriors 50+<br>
<br>
Thoughts? Putting feelers out there since I am rapidly running out of opportunities for the book as I level through 52 and I am going to be putting my own Naggy/Vox raids together soon.<br>
